European Energy Trading Analytics Dashboard (Version 2 — Python Quant Edition)
Project Overview

This project is an advanced Quantitative Energy Trading Analytics Dashboard built using Python (Pandas, NumPy) for data engineering and financial computations, and Power BI for interactive visualization.

It extends a traditional BI dashboard into a quant finance-style analytics system, replicating workflows commonly used in:

Energy trading desks
Risk management teams
Commodity hedge funds
Quantitative analytics roles

The analysis focuses on European energy markets during 2022–2025, covering:

Brent Crude Oil
TTF Natural Gas
EUA Carbon Prices
European Electricity Index
🧠 Project Philosophy
Version 1 (DAX-Based)
Python → Data Cleaning
Power BI → All calculations (DAX)
Version 2 (This Project)
Python → Full quantitative analytics engine
Power BI → Visualization layer only

This version represents a real-world quant workflow where heavy computations are done upstream.

