Correlation Analysis
Brent_TTF rolling correlation (30D)
TTF_Power rolling correlation (30D)
EUA_Power rolling correlation (30D)
Performance Metrics
Sharpe Ratios (252D rolling)
Drawdowns (cumulative peak-to-trough decline)
